#: ../../../index.md:1
msgid "Welcome to VTK's documentation!"
msgstr "歡迎閱讀 VTK 文件！"

#: ../../../index.md:3
msgid ""
"VTK is an open-source software system for image processing, 3D graphics, "
"volume rendering, and visualization. Our documentation is a comprehensive "
"resource for both new and seasoned VTK users and includes tutorials, "
"examples, and best practices to help you unlock the full power of VTK's "
"advanced algorithms and rendering techniques."
msgstr ""
"VTK 是一個用於影像處理、3D 圖形、立體算繪和視覺化的開源軟體系統。我們的文件"
"為 VTK 的新手和資深使用者提供了全面的資源，其中包括教學課程、範例和最佳實踐，"
"旨在幫助您發揮 VTK 進階演算法和算繪技術的全部效能。"

#: ../../../index.md:9
msgid ""
"We invite you to join the VTK community and explore our documentation to "
"find out how you can use VTK to bring your visions to life."
msgstr ""
"我們誠摯邀請您加入 VTK 社群並查閱我們的文件，了解如何利用 VTK 將您的願景化為"
"現實。"

